  }, "v7"), mdx("p", null, "Sau b\u1ED1n n\u0103m \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m th\u01B0a v\u1EDBi vua \u0110a-v\xEDt, \"Xin cho con v\u1EC1 H\u1EBFp-r\xF4n. Con mu\u1ED1n th\u1EF1c hi\u1EC7n \u0111i\u1EC1u con h\u1EE9a nguy\u1EC7n v\u1EDBi CH\xDAA. "), mdx("h6", {
