  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "Trong khi con c\xF2n \u1EDF Gh\xEA-sua trong x\u1EE9 A-ram con th\u01B0a, 'N\u1EBFu CH\xDAA mang t\xF4i v\u1EC1 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem con th\u1EC1 s\u1EBD th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y Ng\xE0i.'\" "), mdx("h6", {
