  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "Vua b\u1EA3o, \"Th\xF4i con h\xE3y \u0111i b\xECnh y\xEAn.\" V\u1EADy \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn H\u1EBFp-r\xF4n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v10"
  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng anh ta b\xED m\u1EADt sai s\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 \u0111i kh\u1EAFp c\xE1c chi t\u1ED9c \xCDt-ra-en. H\u1ECD b\u1EA3o d\xE2n ch\xFAng, \"Khi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i nghe ti\u1EBFng k\xE8n th\xEC h\xE3y la l\xEAn: '\xC1p-xa-l\xF4m \u0111\xE3 l\xEAn l\xE0m vua \u1EDF H\u1EBFp-r\xF4n!'\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v11"
  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "\xC1p-xa-l\xF4m \u0111\xE3 m\u1EDDi hai tr\u0103m ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF9ng \u0111i v\u1EDBi m\xECnh. V\u1EADy h\u1ECD t\u1EEB Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem \u0111i xu\u1ED1ng v\u1EDBi anh nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt \xE2m m\u01B0u c\u1EE7a anh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v12"
  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "Trong khi \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m \u0111ang d\xE2ng c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 th\xEC anh cho m\u1EDDi A-hi-t\xF4-ph\xEAn, m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng c\u1ED1 v\u1EA5n c\u1EE7a \u0110a-v\xEDt, t\u1EEB Ghi-l\xF4, qu\xEA c\u1EE7a \xF4ng \u0111\u1EBFn. \xC2m m\u01B0u c\u1EE7a \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m th\xE0nh c\xF4ng. C\xE0ng ng\xE0y c\xE0ng c\xF3 \u0111\xF4ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u1EE7ng h\u1ED9 anh ta. "), mdx("h6", {
