    "id": "v14"
  }, "v14"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110a-v\xEDt li\u1EC1n b\u1EA3o c\xE1c qu\u1EA7n th\u1EA7n c\xF3 m\u1EB7t v\u1EDBi vua \u1EDF Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem, \"Ch\xFAng ta ph\u1EA3i r\u1EDDi \u0111\xE2y ngay l\u1EADp t\u1EE9c! N\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng ch\xFAng ta s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng tho\xE1t kh\u1ECFi tay \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m. Ch\xFAng ta ph\u1EA3i nhanh ch\xE2n tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi n\xF3 b\u1EAFt k\u1ECBp ch\xFAng ta, gi\u1EBFt ch\xFAng ta c\xF9ng d\xE2n ch\xFAng Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem.\" "), mdx("h6", {
