    "id": "v17"
  }, "v17"), mdx("p", null, "Vua c\xF9ng c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i theo l\xEAn \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng v\xE0 d\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i \u1EDF m\u1ED9t c\u0103n nh\xE0 kh\xE1 xa. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c t\xF4i t\u1EDB vua \u0111i qua tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t vua: ng\u01B0\u1EDDi K\xEA-r\xEA-th\xEDt, v\xE0 B\xEA-l\xEA-th\xEDt, t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u1EDF G\xE1t, v\xE0 s\xE1u tr\u0103m ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE3 theo vua. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v19"
  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Vua b\u1EA3o Y-tai, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi mi\u1EC1n G\xE1t r\u1EB1ng, \"Sao ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111i theo ch\xFAng ta l\xE0m g\xEC? H\xE3y tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 \u1EDF v\u1EDBi vua \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111i v\xEC ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xE0 ngo\u1EA1i ki\u1EC1u. X\u1EE9 n\u1EA7y \u0111\xE2u ph\u1EA3i qu\xEA h\u01B0\u01A1ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE2u. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u01A1i m\u1EDBi theo ta \u0111\xE2y th\xF4i. T\u1EA1i sao ta ph\u1EA3i b\u1EAFt ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111i lang thang v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng ta trong khi ch\xEDnh ta c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt m\xECnh \u0111i \u0111\xE2u n\u1EEFa? H\xE3y tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1, mang c\xE1c anh em ng\u01B0\u01A1i theo ng\u01B0\u01A1i. Nguy\u1EC1n ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta t\u1ECF l\xF2ng nh\xE2n t\u1EEB v\xE0 trung th\xE0nh.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng Y-tai th\u01B0a v\u1EDBi vua, \"T\xF4i th\u1EC1 trong danh CH\xDAA h\u1EB1ng s\u1ED1ng v\xE0 m\u1EA1ng s\u1ED1ng vua, t\xF4i nh\u1EA5t \u0111\u1ECBnh \u1EDF v\u1EDBi vua d\xF9 s\u1ED1ng d\xF9 ch\u1EBFt.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110a-v\xEDt li\u1EC1n b\u1EA3o Y-tai, \"V\u1EADy th\xEC \u0111i.\" V\u1EADy Y-tai ng\u01B0\u1EDDi G\xE1t v\xE0 t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF9ng gia \u0111\xECnh h\u1ECD ti\u1EBFp t\u1EE5c \u0111i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v23"
  }, "v23"), mdx("p", null, "T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 d\xE2n ch\xFAng kh\xF3c l\u1EDBn khi m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i qua. Vua \u0110a-v\xEDt b\u0103ng qua thung l\u0169ng K\xEDt-r\xF4n, r\u1ED3i h\u1ECD ti\u1EBFp t\u1EE5c \u0111i \u0111\u1EBFn sa m\u1EA1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v24"
  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "Xa-\u0111\u1ED1c c\xF9ng m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi L\xEA-vi \u0111i v\u1EDBi \xF4ng khi\xEAng R\u01B0\u01A1ng Giao \u01AF\u1EDBc c\u1EE7a Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF. H\u1ECD \u0111\u1EB7t R\u01B0\u01A1ng xu\u1ED1ng, r\u1ED3i A-bia-tha c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE3 ra kh\u1ECFi th\xE0nh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v25"
