    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng n\u1EBFu CH\xDAA b\u1EA3o Ng\xE0i kh\xF4ng th\xEDch ta n\u1EEFa th\xEC ta \u0111\xE3 s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng. Ng\xE0i mu\u1ED1n x\u1EED ta th\u1EBF n\xE0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v27"
  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "Vua n\xF3i ti\u1EBFp v\u1EDBi Xa-\u0111\u1ED1c l\xE0 th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5, \"Ng\u01B0\u01A1i c\xF3 ph\u1EA3i l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ti\xEAn ki\u1EBFn kh\xF4ng? H\xE3y tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 th\xE0nh b\xECnh y\xEAn v\xE0 mang theo A-hi-m\xE1t, con ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xE0 Gi\xF4-na-than, con A-bia-tha. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD ch\u1EDD n\u01A1i ch\u1ED7 b\u0103ng qua sa m\u1EA1c cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi ta nghe tin t\u1EE9c ng\u01B0\u01A1i b\xE1o.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v29"
  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy Xa-\u0111\u1ED1c v\xE0 A-bia-tha mang R\u01B0\u01A1ng c\u1EE7a Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem v\xE0 \u1EDF l\u1EA1i \u0111\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110a-v\xEDt \u0111i l\xEAn n\xFAi \xD4-liu, v\u1EEBa \u0111i v\u1EEBa kh\xF3c. \xD4ng tr\xF9m \u0111\u1EA7u v\xE0 \u0111i ch\xE2n \u0111\u1EA5t. \u0110o\xE0n ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i v\u1EDBi \xF4ng c\u0169ng tr\xF9m \u0111\u1EA7u v\xE0 v\u1EEBa \u0111i v\u1EEBa kh\xF3c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v31"
  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi b\xE1o cho \u0110a-v\xEDt, \"A-hi-t\xF4-ph\xEAn l\xE0 m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\xE0 \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m tham kh\u1EA3o \xFD ki\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EC3 ph\u1EA3n vua.\" \u0110a-v\xEDt li\u1EC1n c\u1EA7u kh\u1EA9n, \"CH\xDAA \u01A1i, xin khi\u1EBFn m\u01B0u c\u1EE7a A-hi-t\xF4-phen ra ngu d\u1EA1i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "Khi \u0110a-v\xEDt l\xEAn t\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EC9nh n\xFAi n\u01A1i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta th\u01B0\u1EDDng th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF, th\xEC Hu-sai, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xC1c-k\xEDt, \u0111i ra g\u1EB7p vua. \xC1o qu\u1EA7n Hu-sai r\xE1ch t\u1EA3 t\u01A1i, \u0111\u1EA7u \u0111\xEDnh b\u1EE5i \u0111\u1EA5t ch\u1EE9ng t\u1ECF ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111ang th\u1EA3m s\u1EA7u. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v33"
  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110a-v\xEDt b\u1EA3o Hu-sai, \"N\u1EBFu ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111i v\u1EDBi ta, ta s\u1EBD c\xF3 th\xEAm m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi n\u1EEFa ph\u1EA3i lo. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng n\u1EBFu ng\u01B0\u01A1i tr\u1EDF v\xE0o th\xE0nh th\xEC ng\u01B0\u01A1i c\xF3 th\u1EC3 bi\u1EBFn m\u01B0u c\u1EE7a A-hi-t\xF4-ph\xEAn ra v\xF4 d\u1EE5ng. H\xE3y b\u1EA3o \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m r\u1EB1ng, 'T\xF4i l\xE0 t\xF4i t\u1EDB vua. Tr\u01B0\u1EDBc kia t\xF4i ph\u1EE5c v\u1EE5 cha c\u1EE7a b\u1EC7 h\u1EA1, nh\u01B0ng nay t\xF4i s\u1EBD ph\u1EE5c v\u1EE5 b\u1EC7 h\u1EA1.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 Xa-\u0111\u1ED1c v\xE0 A-bia-tha s\u1EBD \u1EDF v\u1EDBi ng\u01B0\u01A1i. H\xE3y thu\u1EADt cho h\u1ECD bi\u1EBFt nh\u1EEFng g\xEC ng\u01B0\u01A1i nghe th\u1EA5y trong cung vua. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
